# --- Contact form delivery ---------------------------------------------------
# The contact form POSTs inquiries to Formspree when this is set.
#
#   1. Create a free form at https://formspree.io
#      (set the notification inbox to info@brillore.co.tz).
#   2. Copy the form endpoint — it looks like: https://formspree.io/f/abcdwxyz
#   3. Paste it below, save this file as ".env" (NOT .env.example), then rebuild.
#
# When left empty, the form gracefully falls back to opening the visitor's mail app.
VITE_FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=
